title: ‘Billions’ Season 5 Finale
description:
Logan Murdock and Wosny Lambre recap the season finale of 'Billions,' “No Direction Home.” The two take a look back at Season 5, discuss the show’s relationship with wealth, and make some predictions for Season 6. 
Hosts: Logan Murdock, Wosny Lambre
Associate Producer: Lani Renaldo
